## Hooks (`hooks/`)

| Hook | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `useTheme` | Returns full `ThemeColors` object |
| `useTranslation` | Returns `{ t, locale, changeLanguage }` |
| `useToast` | Re-exports toast API from `ToastContext` |
| `useAuth` (via AuthContext) | `{ session, user, isLoading, signOut }` |
| `useBibleschoolContent` | Fetches Storyblok bibleschool category |
| `useCompletedLessons` | Lesson completion data for a user |
| `useIntroVideoPosition` | Persists intro video position |
| `useIntroVideoWatched` | Whether user has watched intro |
| `useIsAdmin` | Admin role check |
| `useLastSectionRestore` | Restores last visited drawer section |
| `useLastWatchedLesson` | Last watched lesson data |
| `useLessonUnlocks` | Which lessons are unlocked |
| `useNetworkQuality` | Network quality info |
| `useNotifications` | User notifications list |
| `usePrefetchLessonThumbnails` | Pre-fetches Vimeo thumbnails |
| `useShadows` | Shadow style helper (light/dark aware) |
| `useStepManager` | Multi-step form/flow state |
| `useStreak` | User learning streak data |
| `useUnlockAnimation` | Unlock animation state |
| `useUserBadges` | User earned badges |
| `useUserProfile` | Current user profile (from Supabase) |
| `useVideoSetting` | User video quality preference |
| `useVimeoPlaybackUrl` | Vimeo playback URL for a video ID |
| `useVimeoThumbnail` | Vimeo thumbnail URL for a video ID |
| `use-color-scheme` | System color scheme (RN Appearance) |

