## Supabase Local

| Path | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `supabase/config.toml` | Local Supabase config (`project_id = "faith-app"`) |
| `supabase/migrations/` | SQL migration files (order by filename YYYYMMDDHHMMSS) |
| `supabase/seed.sql` | Dev seed data |
| `supabase/scripts/` | Helper scripts |

Current migrations (in order):
1. `20260218120000_initial_schema.sql` — profiles, progress, quiz, user_settings, RPCs, RLS
2. `20260218140000_badges.sql` — badges, user_badges, user_streaks
3. `20260218150000_user_notifications.sql` — user_notifications, RLS, realtime
4. `20260218160000_user_notifications_delete_policy.sql` — DELETE policy
